com.interpss.core.aclf

Interface BaseAclfNetwork<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<? extends AclfGen,? extends AclfLoad>,TBranch extends AclfBranch>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAreaZone, IAclfNetAdjustment, IAclfNetElement, IAclfNetFormMatrix, IAclfNetFunc, IAdaptable, IMultiNet, INet3WXfrElement, INetBranchElement<TBus,TBranch>, INetBusElement<TBus>, INetworkElement, NameTag, Network<TBus,TBranch>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AclfNetwork, AcscNetwork, BaseAcscNetwork<TBus,TBranch>, BaseDStabNetwork<TBus,TBra>, BaseOpfNetwork, DclfOpfNetwork, DStab3PNetwork, DStabilityNetwork, Dynamic3PNetwork, OpfNetwork, Steady3PNetwork
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfNetworkImpl, AcscNetworkImpl, BaseAclfNetworkImpl, BaseAcscNetworkImpl, BaseDStabNetworkImpl, BaseOpfNetworkImpl, DclfOpfNetworkImpl, DStabilityNetworkImpl, Dynamic3PNetworkImpl, OpfNetworkImpl, Steady3PNetworkImpl

    public interface BaseAclfNetwork<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<? extends AclfGen,? extends AclfLoad>,TBranch extends AclfBranch>
extends Network<TBus,TBranch>, IAclfNetFunc, IAclfNetAdjustment, INet3WXfrElement, IAclfNetElement, IAclfAreaZone, IAclfNetFormMatrix
    A representation of the model object 'Base Aclf Network'. Base AclfNetwork class is for storing network information for implementing AC loadflow analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • Network Type
    • Sensitivity Calculated
    • Lf Data Loaded
    • Lf Converged
    • Zero ZBranch Threshold
    • Xfr ZAdjust Side
    • Default Voltage Limit
    • Zero ZBranch Processed
    • Aclf Net Adjust
    • Xfr ZTable
    • Ps Xfr PControl List
    • Tap Control List
    • Remote QBus List
    • Svc List
    • Special Branch List
    See Also:
    AclfPackage.getBaseAclfNetwork()
